metadata.name: Heedong #1
metadata.description:
Welcome to the Wonderful World of HeeDong™! From the imagination of artist and illustrator Aaron Chang comes the second installment for BBRC Studios, HeeDong™! HeeDong is a collection of 5,555 PFPs of our cute and magical Boston Terrier. All are unique, but some are rarer than others. 

HeeDong is the next pop-cultural icon in the making and next upcoming multi-media franchise to entertain this generation through excellent storytelling, delightful experiences, and innovative technologies powered by Web3. A series of exciting adventures awaits, starting with an exclusive collectible 6” vinyl designed by 7 different notable artists and produced by Mighty Jaxx.

Step into HeeDong’s dreams where his fantasies come to life, adventures are plentiful, imagination is boundless, and anything is possible.

Visit HeeDong at https://www.heedong.io
